  "title": "The Missing Key",
  "genre": "daily",
  "summary": "Leo wakes up late on Monday morning and cannot find his key anywhere.",
  "coverScene": "A young man looks frantically under a messy armchair in his living room while a small cat sits nearby watching him with calm eyes.",
  "levels": {
    "B2": {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo woke up late on Monday morning because his alarm clock had failed to go off.",
              "audioStart": 0.1,
              "audioEnd": 4.3
            },
            {
              "text": "Today was the start of his new job at a large business in the city.",
              "audioStart": 5.162,
              "audioEnd": 8.387
            },
            {
              "text": "He felt very stressed as he realized that he had only thirty minutes to arrive at the office.",
              "audioStart": 9.25,
              "audioEnd": 13.938
            },
            {
              "text": "After he dressed quickly, he reached for his key, but it was not on the table where he always kept it.",
              "audioStart": 14.8,
              "audioEnd": 20.3
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo looked around his apartment, but he could not find the key anywhere.",
              "audioStart": 21.163,
              "audioEnd": 24.725
            },
            {
              "text": "If he had not been so nervous, he would have checked his pockets more carefully.",
              "audioStart": 25.587,
              "audioEnd": 29.613
            },
            {
              "text": "He searched under the bed and behind the sofa, but the important item remained hidden.",
              "audioStart": 30.475,
              "audioEnd": 34.663
            },
            {
              "text": "He thought that he might have left it in the door, yet the door was empty.",
              "audioStart": 35.525,
              "audioEnd": 39.062
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The man began to worry because he had to be on time for his first day.",
              "audioStart": 39.925,
              "audioEnd": 43.475
            },
            {
              "text": "He remembered that he had walked through the living room when he came home yesterday evening.",
              "audioStart": 44.337,
              "audioEnd": 48.462
            },
            {
              "text": "Maybe he had dropped the key while he was taking off his shoes.",
              "audioStart": 49.325,
              "audioEnd": 52.375
            },
            {
              "text": "He decided that he would look inside his sports bag as a last resort.",
              "audioStart": 53.237,
              "audioEnd": 56.825
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "While Leo searched the room, his cat watched him from the top of a wooden chair.",
              "audioStart": 57.688,
              "audioEnd": 61.65
            },
            {
              "text": "The cat was a small animal that seemed to enjoy this strange morning activity.",
              "audioStart": 62.513,
              "audioEnd": 66.325
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo walked toward the corner where his favorite shoes were kept.",
              "audioStart": 67.188,
              "audioEnd": 70.287
            },
            {
              "text": "He noticed that one shoe was moved slightly away from its normal place.",
              "audioStart": 71.15,
              "audioEnd": 74.862
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo picked up the shoe and turned it over.",
              "audioStart": 75.725,
              "audioEnd": 77.8
            },
            {
              "text": "Suddenly, he heard a small sound as something metal fell onto the floor.",
              "audioStart": 78.662,
              "audioEnd": 82.45
            },
            {
              "text": "The missing key had been hidden inside the shoe by the cat during the night.",
              "audioStart": 83.312,
              "audioEnd": 86.763
            },
            {
              "text": "He realized that the cat had played with the key and put it there himself.",
              "audioStart": 87.625,
              "audioEnd": 91.312
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo felt very happy as he picked up the key from the floor.",
              "audioStart": 92.175,
              "audioEnd": 95.2
            },
            {
              "text": "He finally opened the door and ran down the street toward the bus station.",
              "audioStart": 96.062,
              "audioEnd": 99.688
            },
            {
              "text": "Although he was still late, he knew that he would reach the office soon.",
              "audioStart": 100.55,
              "audioEnd": 103.9
            },
            {
              "text": "He promised that he would keep his keys in a safer place in the future.",
              "audioStart": 104.763,
              "audioEnd": 108.312
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "audio": "audio/b2/st-0047.mp3",
